*** Simple Image Crop ***
--------------------------
CHANGELOG
--------------------------

v.0.8.4 (04/26/2013)
- Added live crop preview
- Enabled user to change the success and warning messages in script initialization
- Upgraded the server-side script to resize the image without quality loss
- Made all html elements to be shown by JavaScript so in case JavaScript is not enabled only the 'noscript' message will be displayed
- Commented JavaScript code for easier further development

